config IS31FL3743
	bool "IS31FL3743 LED driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ISSI_IS31FL3743_ENABLED
	select I2C
	help
	  Enable LED driver for IS31FL3743.
	  IS31FL3743 is a matrix LED driver, capable of a maximum of 3.03 mA
	  per LED, or 34.5 mA total across all LEDs in the 18x11 dot matrix.
